was mad, hehe.  But soloing he would way outdamage me because of rapidity of CBoL in mainhand from the front.   So if your grouping, get the high damage/ high delay weapons, ratio is god in offhand until 50ish. then you have to work from other issues.  but 13/26 or 14/28 will be your best bet for uber damage and low proc.   I was BS'ing for 350 at level 35 with SBS(stilleto) and people were like WTF?.  and no, its not really all that slow when you think about it.  the only time i held taunt was if we had pally tanking who wasnt stunning who was wielding a WS or something like that.  /shrug.   Anyhow, just remember, high damage in mainhand, amazing ratio in offhand, thats the key for low/mid leveling as a twink rogue in groups.<br>
